Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Profesorka Minami Amada alias doktorka Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je to špecialistka na robotiku, ktorej veci sa skoro vždy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dostanú do rúk armády.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Som Chen zo spoločnosti Da Xinghai z Hong Kongu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rád vás spoznávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vašou misiou je zaistiť túto ženu, doktorku Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A ak sa vám niekto pokúsi dostať do cesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}... zneškodnite ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koho zaujíma, čo sa stane s doktorkou Amadou Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zredukujem ich
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a venujem ich smrť mojim podriadeným,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ktorých zabil Kasper Hekmatyar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Valmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:00:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo vyskočila von?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci kryte Valmet!
