Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:17.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2.5}yori takaku toberu hou he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}I want to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2.5}mamoritai yo bokura no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:27.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}what our wingless backs here bore
